      "keyPoints": [
        "قَالَ (hollow): قَالَ النَّبِيُّ ﷺ (The Prophet said)",
        "رَوَى (doubly weak): رَوَى الْحَدِيثَ (He narrated the hadith)",
        "صَلَّى (defective): صَلَّى النَّبِيُّ (The Prophet prayed)",
        "هَدَى (defective): هَدَاهُ اللهُ (Allah guided him)",
        "رَضِيَ (defective): رَضِيَ اللهُ عَنْهُ (May Allah be pleased with him)"
      ],
